Name: Fishing Frenzy
About the game: Fishing Frenzy is a very interesting fishing game! You have to fight for prey, catch fish, blow up mad sharks and seahorses, collect stellar fish and shells, catch bubbles and bombs, worms, treasures, watches and gifts. This game has a lot to collect and anything is possible! Make your way to the top and become the best player in this naval battle! Management boat and a fishing rod: the arrow keys left, right, down, or alternatively, the keys A, S, D. Reset bomb: Spacebar. The game is waiting for you: - Cute graphics - Musical accompaniment - Fishing Enjoy the game!
